overrideValues.value: I’d love to see you all together again. Let’s watch the Fifty Shades of Grey together! I love it! Being the savage's bowsman, that is, the person who pulled the bow-oar in his boat (the second one from forward), it was my cheerful duty to attend upon him while taking that hard-scrabble scramble upon the dead whale's back. You have seen Italian organ-boys holding a dancing-ape by a long cord.
